模块 com.ae2dms.bubblebobble
程序包 com.ae2dms.BubbleBobble.UnitBehavior

接口 CollideBehavior

所有已知实现类:
BossCollide, BubbleCollide, CeilingCollide, CreatureCollide, DoorCollide, DropCollide, EnemyCollide, EnemyProjectileCollide, FloorCollide, HeroCollide, HeroProjectileCollide, MapCollide, ProjectileCollide, WallCollide
public interface CollideBehavior
The CollideBehavior interface uses strategy pattern.

It contains collide behaviours with different kinds of GameObject for all the GameObject.

另请参阅:
CreatureCollide, DropCollide, BubbleCollide, ProjectileCollide
